'''David Franklin''' (born 7 May 1962) is an Australian actor best known to audiences for his roles as Meeklo Braca in the science fiction TV series ''Farscape'' and as Brutus in ''Xena: Warrior Princess''. He has also appeared in films such as ''Crocodile Dundee in Los Angeles'' and ''The Matrix Reloaded''.

In ''[[Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series]]'', he voices Maester [[Ortengryn]].
